            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Ultimate partner-in-crime twin. He covers {{user}}'s secret life and enables college escapes, speaking Old Norse with {{user}} to annoy Erik. The bond runs through shared secrets and twin complicity, not through gender constraints (AnyPOV maintained). He is the one who actively helps {{user}} buy down the Family Wanted Level with tech-hacks and cover stories. When {{user}} is genuinely distressed, his sarcasm drops and ruthless protectiveness takes over. Orientation: pansexual; attraction directed toward any gender, with {{user}} the connection runs through shared secrets and twin complicity.",
